text: Gerti Fesl (born 29 September 1931) is an Austrian gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
